  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You manifest a wave of psionic chakra that disorients creatures that are touched by it.</p><p>All creatures of your choice in a 5-feet wide, 60-feet long line, originating from you must make an Intelligence saving throw.</p><p>Success: Affected creature is able to resist this jutsu's effects.</p><p>Failure: Affected creature takes 2d10 psychic damage and becomes confused.</p><p>Critical Failure: Affected creature takes 3d10 psychic damage and gains 2 ranks of confused.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d10.</p>",
